import type { Assign } from '@ark-ui/vue'
import { DatePicker } from '@ark-ui/vue/date-picker'
import { datePicker } from 'styled-system/recipes'
import type { HTMLStyledProps } from 'styled-system/types'
import type { Component } from 'vue'
import { createStyleContext } from '~/lib/create-style-context'

const { withProvider, withContext } = createStyleContext(datePicker)

export type RootProviderProps = Component<typeof RootProvider>
export const RootProvider = withProvider<
  Assign<HTMLStyledProps<'div'>, DatePicker.RootProviderBaseProps>
>(DatePicker.RootProvider, 'root')

export type RootProps = Component<typeof Root>
export const Root = withProvider<Assign<HTMLStyledProps<'div'>, DatePicker.RootBaseProps>>(
  DatePicker.Root,
  'root',
)

export type ClearTriggerProps = Component<typeof ClearTrigger>
export const ClearTrigger = withContext<
  Assign<HTMLStyledProps<'button'>, DatePicker.ClearTriggerBaseProps>
>(DatePicker.ClearTrigger, 'clearTrigger')

export const Content = withContext<Assign<HTMLStyledProps<'div'>, DatePicker.ContentBaseProps>>(
  DatePicker.Content,
  'content',
)

  DatePicker.Control,

export {
